title: Bruceville Meadows
description: Tentative subdivision map to divide 113.9± acres into ~320 single family residential lots, one multifamily lot, a detention basin, drainage channel, two pocket parks, and various landscape lots. The Project also includes an amendment to the SEPA Strategic Plan to reduce the single family residential density.
